OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1782404310
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FKris Jepson reports from Teesside
OL,7,FCrown Court where two people are on
OL,8,Ftrial accused of the murder of two-
OL,9,Fyear-old Isabelle Welsh
OL,11,F*Warning - this article includes
OL,12,Fdistressing content
OL,14,FA toddler whose mother and her new
OL,15,Fboyfriend are accused of her murder
OL,16,Fand sexual assault suffered 21 broken
OL,17,Fbones in the weeks leading up to her
OL,18,Fdeath, a court heard.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
