PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1782404310
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FIsabelle Welsh, two, collapsed at her
OL,7,Fhome in Hartington Close, Thornaby,
OL,8,FTeesside, having suffered a "massive
OL,9,Fhead injury", and could not be saved,
OL,10,Fjurors were told.
OL,12,FHer mother, Alexandra Walker, 25, and
OL,13,FHarrison Simpson, 22, deny murder,
OL,14,Fallowing the death of a child, sexual
OL,15,Fassault and child cruelty and are on
OL,16,Ftrial at Teesside Crown Court.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1782404310
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FThe couple had got together only last
OL,7,Fsummer and Simpson became a regular
OL,8,Fvisitor to Walker's home, spending "a
OL,9,Flot of time" with the little girl,
OL,10,Fjurors were told.
OL,12,FOn 13 September 2025, Walker made a
OL,13,F999 call about her daughter who had
OL,14,Fcollapsed, and paramedics found
OL,15,FIsabelle at the foot of the stairs,
OL,16,Fwithout a pulse and gravely ill.
OL,26,@pD@dOUqD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1782404310
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FRichard Wright KC, prosecuting, said
OL,7,Fshe was covered in bruises,
OL,8,Fparticularly to her head, neck,
OL,9,Fabdomen, back and private parts, her
OL,10,Fnappy contained blood and she had
OL,11,Fvomit on her face.
OL,13,FShe was rushed to hospital by
OL,14,Fambulance, but despite the efforts of
OL,15,Fspecialist doctors, she died in the
OL,16,Fearly hours of 14 September.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
