PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1782404310
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FThe prosecution said Isabelle had been
OL,7,Fviolently shaken, her spine over-
OL,8,Fextended, and her head hit against a
OL,9,Fhard surface such as a wall or the
OL,10,Ffloor.
OL,12,FMr Wright said: "For weeks this child
OL,13,Fhad been violently assaulted and her
OL,14,Fdeath, by that terrible head injury,
OL,15,Fwas simply the end point in that
OL,16,Fcampaign of violence to which she had
OL,17,Fbeen subjected."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1782404310
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FThe prosecution case was that both
OL,7,FWalker and Simpson had "ample
OL,8,Fopportunity" to harm the toddler and
OL,9,Fin such a small, two-bedroom house
OL,10,F"each must have been aware of the
OL,11,Fabuse".
OL,13,FMr Wright said Walker took her
OL,14,Fdaughter to the GP and then hospital
OL,15,F11 days before she died, when
OL,16,FIsabelle's leg was found to be
OL,17,Ffractured, and despite the concerns of
OL,18,Fsome medics, she was discharged back
OL,19,Finto her mother's care.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1782404310
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FThe prosecution said this leg fracture
OL,7,Fwas "no more of an accident than the
OL,8,Ffatal head injury".
OL,10,FA post mortem examination found that
OL,11,FIsabelle had suffered fractures to 21
OL,12,Fbones and she was "covered in bruising
OL,13,Fthe result of forceful gripping", Mr
OL,14,FWright said.
OL,16,FThe prosecution said Walker, by her
OL,17,Fown account, had waited two weeks
OL,18,Fbefore reporting the fractured leg.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1782404310
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FMr Wright said: "When Isabelle was
OL,7,Fgravely unwell in the week before she
OL,8,Fdied no medical assistance was sought,
OL,9,Fand even on the day she died, after
OL,10,Fher heart had stopped and she appeared
OL,11,Fto all intents and purposes to be
OL,12,Fdead, Alexandra Walker only called an
OL,13,Fambulance when her stepfather told her
OL,14,Fto, long after she must have known her
OL,15,Fdaughter was critically ill.
OL,17,F"All of this, we will invite you to
OL,18,Fconclude, was not because of panic
OL,19,Fabout Isabelle, or a failure to
OL,20,Fappreciate how ill she was.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1782404310
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,F"To the contrary, Alexandra Walker and
OL,7,FHarrison Simpson each plainly knew how
OL,8,Fill she was, they knew that because
OL,9,Fthey had caused her injuries and their
OL,10,Ffailure to summon help from doctors
OL,11,Fand finally the emergency services,
OL,12,Fwas an act of self-preservation.
OL,14,F"They knew the questions that would
OL,15,Fcome and had no convincing answer for
OL,16,Fthem."
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/15
