PN,39911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1782404310
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FMr Wright read an early message from
OL,7,FWalker to her new boyfriend in which
OL,8,Fshe said she was the primary carer for
OL,9,Fher daughter and was in the final year
OL,10,Fof studying forensics.
OL,12,FMr Wright read a message between
OL,13,FWalker and her mother which discussed
OL,14,Fthe defendant apparently calling
OL,15,FSimpson a "paedo".
OL,17,FWalker also referred to Simpson not
OL,18,Fwanting to spend time with her alone
OL,19,Fand preferred to see her and Isabelle,
OL,20,Ftelling her mother: "It's weird".
OL,26,@wD@KOUwD@QO]|D@UOU|D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1782404310
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FAnd in other messages with her mother,
OL,7,FWalker referred to Simpson as "a
OL,8,Fhomeless romance scammer".
OL,10,FThe jury was also shown images from a
OL,11,Fcamera in the house which showed
OL,12,FWalker intoxicated in her kitchen,
OL,13,Fjabbing herself with a knife, while
OL,14,Fshe was supposed to be caring for her
OL,15,Fdaughter.
OL,17,FMr Wright said Walker used her phone
OL,18,Fto search the sex offenders register
OL,19,Fin Middlesbrough in August last year.
OL,26,@oD@_OUpD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1782404310
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FHe said the context of the search was
OL,7,Fthat Walker was concerned about
OL,8,FSimpson's interaction with her
OL,9,Fdaughter.
OL,11,FMr Wright said Walker had discussed
OL,12,Fwith her mother how Simpson had bathed
OL,13,FIsabelle when he was alone, looking
OL,14,Fafter the toddler.
OL,16,FWalker's mother Claire was heard on
OL,17,FCCTV footage expressing concern about
OL,18,FIsabelle days after she had been
OL,19,Fadmitted to hospital with a broken leg.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
