PN,39914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1782404310
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FThe grandmother said to Walker: "She
OL,7,Flooks like she is being abused."
OL,9,FLater, the daughter told her mother to
OL,10,F"chill out", to which the concerned
OL,11,Fgrandmother replied: "I cannot help
OL,12,Fbut be worried."
OL,14,FThe prosecution suggested that Walker
OL,15,Fwas defensive because she knew
OL,16,Fprecisely why Isabelle was so unwell,
OL,17,Fand because she was concerned that
OL,18,Fsuspicion would fall back on her and
OL,19,Fher boyfriend.
OL,26,@nD@aOUoD@`O]rD@AOUrD@KO]sD@VOUtD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G14/15
