OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FWalker and Simpson deny all charges
OL,7,Fand the trial at Teesside Crown Court
OL,8,Fcontinues on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G15/15
